  <h1>Help & Support</h1>
  <p>Need assistance? We're here to help. Below are answers to some common questions about NergNet.</p>

  <h2>ðŸ“Œ Common Questions</h2>

  <h3>1. I didnâ€™t receive my referral bonus. Why?</h3>
  <p>Referral bonuses are granted when the referred user signs up using your referral ID and successfully creates a wallet. If there was a typo or missing field, the bonus might not be credited.</p>

  <h3>2. My mining isn't starting. What can I do?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Ensure you are signed into your account</li>
    <li>Check your internet connection</li>
    <li>Try restarting the app</li>
    <li>Make sure your wallet is properly set up</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>3. How do I check my NERG balance?</h3>
  <p>Go to the <strong>Dashboard</strong> in the app. Your live balance, mining rewards, and bonus history are displayed there in real time.</p>

  <h3>4. Can I withdraw or transfer NERG?</h3>
  <p>NERG is currently used within the app. Future updates may allow transfers to external wallets or exchanges.</p>

  <h3>5. Where can I see my transaction history?</h3>
  <p>Tap the <strong>Transactions</strong> tab. All mining rewards, bonuses, and earnings are recorded there with timestamps.</p>

  <h3>6. What if I find a bug?</h3>
  <p>We appreciate your feedback! Please report bugs to <a href="mailto:support@nergnet.app">support@nergnet.app</a> or via our Telegram group.</p>

